            "grid_image_size": "square",
            "heading": "",
            "text": "<h6>Exploring Designs</h6><p>It’s time to delve into your jewellery design details! You can view our existing jewellery in person, online, or via the online builder. Once your stone and setting details are decided, we will start sourcing your unique gemstones!</p>",
