            "image": "shopify://shop_images/heating-metal-ring.jpg",
            "grid_image_size": "square",
            "heading": "",
            "text": "<h6>The Crafting Process</h6><p>Your stunning jewellery is cast, hand set, and finished by our skilled UK based jewellers. We meticulously check every detail is perfect, add any personalisation you've chosen, and then your ring is carefully prepared for its journey to you.</p>",
            "button_link": "",
            "button_text": ""
          }
        }
