        "image_max_width": 120,
        "additional_text": "Rated 5 stars by 100s of Clients in Chichester & Beyond",
        "title": "Luxury That Speaks for Itself.",
        "description": "<p>Each piece we create tells a story—of beauty, elegance, and trust. But don't just take our word for it. Discover how our timeless craftsmanship has left a lasting impression on jewellery lovers around the world. </p><p></p><p><a href=\"/pages/reviews\" title=\"Our Customer Reviews\">View All Reviews</a></p>",
